        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-11" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;FGameplayAbilityActorInfo&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt; 어빌리티가 자주 접근해야 하는 소유 액터(Owning Actor)의 데이터 캐시 (이동 컴포넌트, 메시 컴포넌트, 애니메이션 인스턴스 등)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;FGameplayAbilityActorInfo&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot;&gt;어빌리티를 사용하는 액터와 관련된 &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;19&quot;&gt;캐시된 데이터&lt;/b&gt;입니다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0,0,0&quot;&gt;InitFromActor 함수를 통해 AActor*로부터 초기화됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0,0,0&quot;&gt;어빌리티는 이를 통해 어떤 액터를 대상으로 동작할지 파악합니다. (예: 특정 액터 클래스에 종속/결합되지 않도록 함)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0,0,0&quot;&gt;다형성(Polymorphism)을 지원하기 위해 주로 포인터 형태로 전달됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0,0,0&quot;&gt;프로젝트의 필요에 따라 &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;13&quot;&gt;UAbilitySystemGlobals::AllocAbilityActorInfo&lt;/code&gt;를 재정의하여 생성되는 기본 구조체 타입을 변경할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;strokeColor=#00CC66;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="620" y="90" width="350" height="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-13" value="&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;* FGameplayAbilityActorInfo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;내가 속한 Actor 와 SkeletalMeshComponent, MovementComponent PlayController 등을 캐싱.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;* OnDestroyed 에 ASC 를 등록 ( 액터가 파괴 될 때 호출 )&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;* 생성될 때 Component 에 더티 체크 -&amp;gt; 파되 될때 더티 체크 해제&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1110" y="140" width="549" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-15" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;entryX=0;entryY=0.25;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" parent="1" source="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-4" target="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-11" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-19" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" parent="1" source="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-17" target="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-18" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-17" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;FActiveGameplayEffectsContainer ActiveGameplayEffects&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;현재 이 컴포넌트에서 활성화된 모든 게임플레이 이펙트가 포함되어 있습니다.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,0,0&quot;&gt;활성 게임플레이 이펙트 컨테이너 (Active GameplayEffects Container)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0,0,0&quot;&gt;활성 게임플레이 이펙트(ActiveGameplayEffects)의 바구니(Bucket) 역할을 함&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0,0,0&quot;&gt;FFastArraySerialization을 구현하는 데 필요함&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;1,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,3,0,0,0&quot;&gt;이 구조체는 UAbilitySystemComponent에서만 사용해야 합니다. FFastArraySerializer를 구현하기 위해 별도의 USTRUCT가 필요한 상황을 제외하면, 이 모든 내용은 UAbilitySystemComponent에 포함될 수 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0,0&quot;&gt;ActiveGameplayEffectContainer를 순회할 때는 CreateConstIterator/CreateIterator 또는 STL 스타일의 범위 기반 반복문을 사용하는 것이 권장됩니다:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0,0,0&quot;&gt;for (const FActiveGameplayEffect&amp;amp; Effect : this) {}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0&quot;&gt;for (auto It = CreateConstIterator(); It; ++It) {}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;strokeColor=#00CC66;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="620" y="490" width="370" height="450" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-18" value="&lt;div&gt;/** 현재 활성화된 이펙트 목록입니다. (내부 함수를 포함하여) 이 변수에 직접 접근하지 마십시오! GetNumGameplayEffect() / GetGameplayEffect()를 사용하십시오! */&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;TArray&amp;lt;FActiveGameplayEffect&amp;gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;GameplayEffects_Internal;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#00CC66;gradientColor=none;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1090" y="480" width="430" height="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-20" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;for (const FActiveGameplayEffect&amp;amp; Effect : GameplayEffectsContainer)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;if (Effect.bPendingRepOnActiveGC)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;{&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;InvokeGameplayCueEvent(Effect.Spec, EGameplayCueEvent::OnActive);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;if (Effect.bPendingRepWhileActiveGC)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;{&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;InvokeGameplayCueEvent(Effect.Spec, EGameplayCueEvent::WhileActive);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#00CC66;gradientColor=none;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1040" y="1310" width="560" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-25" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" parent="1" source="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-21" target="nYRWSuvBfACys_Zh3A_y-24" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
